    <title>Sandwich Recipe</title>
	<link href="~/css/sandwich.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

  

    <div class="recipe-container">
        <h1>Easy & Delicious Veg Sandwich Recipe</h1>
        <img src="images/sandwich.jpg" alt="Sandwich" class="recipe-image">

        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>4 Bread Slices</li>
            <li>1/2 cup Cucumber (sliced)</li>
            <li>1/2 cup Tomato (sliced)</li>
            <li>1/2 cup Onion (sliced)</li>
            <li>1/4 cup Bell Pepper (sliced)</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Butter</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Mayonnaise</li>
            <li>1 tsp Black Pepper Powder</li>
            <li>1 tsp Chaat Masala</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Butter the bread slices on both sides.</li>
            <li>Spread mayonnaise on one side of each slice.</li>
            <li>Layer cucumber, tomato, onion, and bell pepper slices.</li>
            <li>Sprinkle black pepper powder, chaat masala, and salt.</li>
            <li>Place another slice on top and grill for 2-3 minutes.</li>
            <li>Cut diagonally and serve with ketchup or green chutney.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
